```plantuml
@startuml microsoft_covid19-BackToWork

actor User
participant "Healthcare Bot" as Bot
participant "Azure Function\nPostUserInfo" as PostUserInfo
participant "Azure Function\nPostSymptomsInfo" as PostSymptomsInfo
participant "Azure Function\nPostLabTestInfo" as PostLabTestInfo
participant "Azure SQL Database" as Database
participant "Azure Function\nTriggerNotification" as TriggerNotification
participant "Notification System" as Notification

User -> Bot: Enter Personal Info
Bot -> PostUserInfo: Send Personal Info
PostUserInfo -> Database: Store Personal Info
Database -> PostUserInfo: Ack
PostUserInfo -> Bot: Ack

User -> Bot: Enter Symptoms Info
Bot -> PostSymptomsInfo: Send Symptoms Info
PostSymptomsInfo -> Database: Store Symptoms Info
Database -> PostSymptomsInfo: Ack
PostSymptomsInfo -> Bot: Ack

User -> Bot: Enter Lab Test Info
Bot -> PostLabTestInfo: Send Lab Test Info
PostLabTestInfo -> Database: Store Lab Test Info
Database -> PostLabTestInfo: Ack
PostLabTestInfo -> Bot: Ack

Bot -> Bot: Assess Health Status

alt Cleared
    Bot -> TriggerNotification: Trigger Notification
    TriggerNotification -> Notification: Send Email with QR Code
end

@enduml
```